item.description: Our 6th Festival / Championship - Official preliminaries to the World Cup held in Buenos Aires - 26 to 28 April 2019 As Event supervisor and Partner, I have been involved since the very beginning and seen this event grow fast to become a major tango event in Europe. Features 5 Milongas in the stunning Porchester Hall 2 after milongas, in the iconic Paddington station and on a boat sailing the Thames A total of 33 hours of social dancing!
